ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAgreement on Mutual Assistance Between their Customs Administrations - Canada - Republic of South Africa **RATIFICATION**
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA regarding Mutual Assistance between their Customs Administrations.
